author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
Deftones have announced that a new album "Private Music" will be released  next month and "My Mind Is A Mountain" is the first single taken from it. I liked it, but need help to describe its genre. We had some issues with copyright on this, so please listen to the song in its entirety (link is below).
I'd also like to apologise for my squeaky chair in this episode. I will sort it out. 

To listen to "My Mind is A Mountain" in its entirety, you can find it here: https://youtu.be/cgh_jEm5twE?si=UkghnqikttTh7cfz
